      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey BioGen, I just went through your latest R&D priority report. I'm seeing a massive skew. Almost all your top-tier therapeutic targets are for conditions that primarily affect Western, Caucasian demographics. We're getting a lot of heat from the board about the lack of focus on diseases prevalent in the Global South. Can you explain why the data is leaning so heavily toward these specific populations?",
